## Added
* F.L.E.I.J.A nuke, Balefire nuke
* ANY vanilla explosion now create cloud and smoke particles
  * For some reason this effect was in the old versions of minecraft but not in 1.21.1
  * Check this video for showcase https://www.reddit.com/r/Minecraft/comments/1mp049m/after_6_years_mojang_has_finally_fixed_the/

## Changed
* Some collisions
* Ivy mike and tsar bomba now will use explosive lenses instead of EARLY explosive lenses
  * Also changed texture of the explosive lenses
* Improved gibbing
  * Iron golems now also turn into metal instead of fleshy chunks
  * Slimes can now be gibbed, turning into slime globs
  * Creepers now also gib into slime instead of blood
* Item renderer translations
* Updated textures for some nuclear bomb GUIs

## Fixed
* Lightning issues in multiblocks
* Spectator now can access multiblock's menu from any part
* 256k fluid tank's render crashing on clients without iris
* Multi detonator missing name and description
* Some explosion block not being ignited by redstone on place